        "description": "<p>Bio-Well combined with the Sputnik sensor provides a structured, objective approach to understanding how environments influence human energy.<br/></p><p>By transforming intuitive perceptions into measurable data, the system supports responsible decision-making, spatial optimization, and interdisciplinary research.<br/></p><p>Designed for practitioners and researchers, the Geobiology Pack enables a consistent, data-driven exploration of environmental energy.</p>",
